PREHEAT oven to 350 degrees F. SPRINKLE almonds over bottom of crust; press in. COMBINE egg, pumpkin, sugar and pumpkin pie spice in medium bowl. Spread over bottom of pie shell. COMBINE corn syrup, eggs, sugar, butter and almond extract in medium bowl; stir in almonds. Spoon over pumpkin layer. BAKE for 50 to 55 minutes or until filling is set. Cool on wire rack.